      "start_time": 138.2,
      "recording_attendee_id": "75158cf1-fa2a-4197-89c0-4ec2baadfc09",
      "order_number": 20,
      "text": "Oh no, I'm, I'm doing good. It's all right. I appreciate you reaching out. Um but I'm not really sure this is regarding"
