      "start_time": 145.83,
      "recording_attendee_id": "6a1fc8ef-f173-4c67-9bf3-f252164d4dd2",
      "order_number": 21,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah. So I'm calling with rentable um formerly a boat. Oh, not sure if you've seen anything on a boat. Oh, um but we are an internet listing service and with a partnership with facebook facebook marketplace. And then we"
