      "recording_attendee_id": "6a1fc8ef-f173-4c67-9bf3-f252164d4dd2",
      "order_number": 22,
      "text": "have our facebook rental ads. Um and also our facebook chat pot, that's pre qualifying all leads. I know from past conversations with Sally that you guys do a lot of your facebook in house and we've been in conversations in the past um but"
