      "recording_id": "4b9f582c-f6f9-475d-a10c-bc4059aa2ae0",
      "end_time": 207.57,
      "start_time": 180.2,
      "recording_attendee_id": "6a1fc8ef-f173-4c67-9bf3-f252164d4dd2",
      "order_number": 24,
      "text": "wanted to just reach out prior to the holidays and see if it might be something that that you would be open to discussing further. I know obviously next week um is a tight window um but wanted to see if there's maybe any time that you had tomorrow, maybe early next week To see you know what we have to offer. And sally had mentioned that you're you're revisiting marketing plans in early two thousand and twenty-one So just wanted to to get us out in front of you to see if it might make sense."
